            "id": "4449286",
            "title": "Troilus secures $35M loan facility to advance pre-development activities",
            "description": "<html><body><ul> <li>Troilus Gold (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TLG:CA\" title=\"Troilus Gold Corp.\">TLG:CA</a></span>) has secured a loan agreement of up to $35M with Auramet International.</li> <li>This non-dilutive facility will support Troilus’ near-term development activities, including final permitting, early works preparation, and advancement toward full project financing.</li> <li>An initial tranche of $15M was advanced to Troilus upon execution of the loan agreement. The remaining $20M will be available for drawdown 90 days from the date of the initial advance and subject to the satisfaction by Troilus of certain conditions precedent.</li> <li>The loan bears 1.0% monthly interest on the outstanding balance, including principal and accrued interest, and is secured by a negative pledge on the company’s assets, a security interest and a hypothec charging personal property of the company.</li> <li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20106871-troilus-secures-us-35-million-loan-facility-to-advance-pre-development-activities\">Press Release</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/assets/og_image_1200-29b2bfe1a595477db6826bd2126c63ac2091efb7ec76347a8e7f81ba17e3de6c.png",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4449286-troilus-secures-35m-loan-facility-to-advance-pre-development-activities",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 05:26:19",
