            "id": "4449244",
            "title": "Carl Icahn boosts stakes in CVR Energy, JetBlue, Illumina, among Q1 trades",
            "description": "<html><body><p>Carl Icahn, once known for his aggressive activism, boosted his stakes in CVR Energy (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CVI\" title=\"CVR Energy, Inc.\">CVI</a>), JetBlue (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JBLU\" title=\"JetBlue Airways Corporation\">JBLU</a>), Illumina (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ILMN\" title=\"Illumina, Inc.\">ILMN</a>), and CVR Partners (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UAN\" title=\"CVR Partners, LP Common Units\">UAN</a>), according to his latest 13F filing.</p>\n<p>Icahn increased his stakes in: CVR Energy (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CVI\" title=\"CVR Energy, Inc.\">CVI</a>) to 68.5M shares with a value of $1.33B at March 31, 2025, from about 66.7M shares; JetBlue (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JBLU\" title=\"JetBlue Airways Corporation\">JBLU</a>) to 33.6M shares ($162.1M) from 17.7M; Illumina (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ILMN\" title=\"Illumina, Inc.\">ILMN</a>) to 220K shares ($17.5M) from 40K shares; and CVR Partners (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UAN\" title=\"CVR Partners, LP Common Units\">UAN</a>) to ~4.10M shares ($308.1M) from ~564.4M shares.</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, the investor reduced his holdings in Southwest Gas (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SWX\" title=\"Southwest Gas Holdings, Inc.\">SWX</a>) to 7.53M shares ($540.8M) from 9.63M in the prior quarter, according to the <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/921669/000153949725001390/xslForm13F_X02/infotable.xml\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"filings.\">filings.</a></p>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/495511756/image_495511756.jpg?io=getty-c-w750",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4449244-carl-icahn-boosts-stakes-in-cvr-energy-jetblue-illumina-among-q1-trades",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 05:21:26",
            "source": "seekalpha",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
