            "id": "4449263",
            "title": "Travere gets FDA review acceptance for expanded approval of Filspari",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Travere Therapeutics (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TVTX\" title=\"Travere Therapeutics, Inc.\">TVTX</a></span>) said on Thursday that the U.S. FDA has accepted its expanded marketing application for traditional approval of Filspari to treat focal segmental glomerulosclerosis, a kidney disease.</li>\n<li>The FDA has assigned a target action date of January 13, 2026.</li>\n<li>The submission for the application is supported by results from the late-stage and mid-stage study for the treatment, the company <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20106622-travere-therapeutics-announces-fda-acceptance-of-snda-for-filspari-sparsentan-in-fsgs\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"said\">said</a>.</li>\n<li>Filspari is also indicated to slow kidney function decline in adults with primary immunoglobulin A nephropathy who are at risk for disease progression.</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346354281/image_1346354281.jpg?io=getty-c-w750",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4449263-travere-gets-fda-review-acceptance-for-expanded-approval-of-filspari",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 05:16:17",
            "source": "seekalpha",
