            "title": "Kadant authorizes repurchase of up to $50M of its shares",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Kadant (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KAI\" title=\"Kadant Inc.\">KAI</a></span>) has authorized the repurchase of up to $50M of its equity securities effective May 15, 2025 through May 15, 2026.</li>\n<li>Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20106747-kadant-authorizes-share-repurchase\">Press release</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
