            "id": "4449194",
            "title": "Soros Fund adds Redfin, Las Vegas Sands, exits Alibaba, AstraZeneca, others in Q1",
            "description": "<html><body><p>Soros Fund Management, the family office founded by billionaire investor George Soros, took fresh stakes in Las Vegas Sands (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LVS\" title=\"Las Vegas Sands Corp.\">LVS</a>), with 807K shares, Redfin (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RDFN\" title=\"Redfin Corporation\">RDFN</a>), with 870.2K shares, and SailPoint (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SAIL\" title=\"SailPoint, Inc.\">SAIL</a>), with 1.04M shares, during the first quarter of 2025, according to a 13F filing dated Thursday.</p>\n<p>On the other hand, the firm dumped its holdings in Alibaba Group Holding (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BABA\" title=\"Alibaba Group Holding Limited\">BABA</a>), AstraZeneca (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AZN\" title=\"AstraZeneca PLC\">AZN</a>), Atlantic Union Bankshares (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AUB\" title=\"Atlantic Union Bankshares Corporation\">AUB</a>) and The Cooper companies (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COO\" title=\"The Cooper Companies, Inc.\">COO</a>).</p>\n<p>Among its reduced positions include Smurfit Westrock (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SW\" title=\"Smurfit Westrock Plc\">SW</a>), to 6.85M shares in Q1 from 7.05M shares in Q4 2024, and Pacific Biosciences of California (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PACB\" title=\"Pacific Biosciences of California, Inc.\">PACB</a>), to 1.00M from 2.37M.</p>\n<p>Soros also boosted its stakes in Aurora Innovation (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AUR\" title=\"Aurora Innovation, Inc.\">AUR</a>), to 2.36M from 868K, Teck Resources (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TECK\" title=\"Teck Resources Limited\">TECK</a>), to 667.8K from 347.2K, and ATI (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ATI\" title=\"ATI Inc.\">ATI</a>), to 613.9K from 391.5K, the <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1029160/000090266425002391/xslForm13F_X02/infotable.xml\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"filing\">filing</a> showed.</p>\n</body></html>",
